		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Excuse my impatience - I could quickly test this when I get home.
<br />
<br />When there are 9 sprites on the same line, which sprite is not drawn?  Is it the one with the highest OAM address?  Or is it the one with the highest X coordinate?

		

		</td>
